Subject: [PATCH] vfio/xe: Reorganize the init to decouple migration from reset
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1012628 CVE-2026-31601 bsc#1263722
Patch-mainline: 7.0.1
Git-commit: 1b81ed612e12ea9df8c5cb6f0ddd4419fd0b8ac8

commit 1b81ed612e12ea9df8c5cb6f0ddd4419fd0b8ac8 upstream.

